<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>맨디 렌 카트론(Mandy Len Catron)</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/mandy_len_catron_falling_in_love_is_the_easy_part?language=ko' lang='ko'>
사랑에 빠지는 건 쉽습니다
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Sep 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Fascinating, Beautiful
</span>
</span>
</div>
